%Vl(High_Single_Line_Subline_Rating,180,126,132,18,8)%aL%?rr<uuuuu|vuuuu|wuuuu|wvuuu|wwuuu|wwvuu|wwwuu|wwwvu|wwwwu|wwwwv|wwwww>
